    <h1>Meet the <span>Urban Observatory Compare App.</span></h1>
    
    <div class="grid-60 alpha">
    <p>This app brings LIVE maps from tons of cities right to your mobile device. So you can compare cool facts about multiple cities anywhere, anytime. (Caution, it’s addictive.)</p>
