    <h1>Get Involved</h1>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="grid-50">
  
<p>Interested in getting your city involved in the Urban Observatory? Have data you’d like to share?</p>

<p><strong>We'd really like to hear from you!</strong></p>

    <p>Beginning February 2015, the Urban Observatory will be on permanent display at the <a href="http://www.si.edu/">Smithsonian Institution</a><span class="txt-red">.</span> This is your chance to get involved in this historic exhibit. (C’mon, we know you’re intrigued.)</p>

